[{"id":"VR876711","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a horizontal rectangle with a pattern of equidistant alternating black and white stripes. A total of eight black stripes and seven white stripes are shown. The central white stripe is labeled Central Bright Fringe. The distance between the center of the white stripe immediately to the left of the central bright fringe, and the center of the white stripe third to the right of the central bright fringe, is x.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR876711.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A laser beam of wavelength <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"lambda\"><math alttext=\"lambda\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>λ</mi></math></span></span> is incident on two narrow, parallel slits. A pattern of alternating bright and dark fringes appears on a distant screen, as shown in the figure. The screen is a distance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"D\"><math alttext=\"D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>D</mi></math></span></span> from the slits, and the center-to-center distance between the two bright fringes indicated is <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi></math></span></span>, where <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x is much smaller than D\"><math alttext=\"x is much smaller than D\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>x</mi><mo>≪</mo><mi>D</mi></math></span></span>. How far apart are the two slits from each other?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR876711_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the fraction lambda D over x\"><math alttext=\"the fraction lambda D over x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 times the fraction lambda D over x\"><math alttext=\"2 times the fraction lambda D over x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 times the fraction lambda D over x\"><math alttext=\"3 times the fraction lambda D over x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"4 times the fraction lambda D over x\"><math alttext=\"4 times the fraction lambda D over x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mn>4</mn><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mi>D</mi></mrow><mi>x</mi></mfrac></mstyle></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":3}]